| Operation        | Method | URL                                |
| ---------------- | ------ | ---------------------------------- |
| Get all recipes  | GET    | `http://localhost:7000/recipe`     |
| Get recipe by ID | GET    | `http://localhost:7000/recipe/:id` |
| Edit recipe      | PUT    | `http://localhost:7000/recipe/:id` |
| Delete recipe    | DELETE | `http://localhost:7000/recipe/:id` |
| Add recipe       | POST   | `http://localhost:7000/recipe`     |
